{"tid":1024843,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"做交通津貼熱線，冇乜野做之餘，仲可以返工係位賭錢，咪話唔爽！","createTime":"2019-02-17T01:06:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T15:49:01.000Z","uid":55950,"like":56,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"4586eded86e940fb7d27f57ad2e16e1c959f5b70","tid":1024843,"uid":55950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T01:06:41.000Z","msg":"是咁的，新年上左阿嬸屋企拜年,咁啱佢有個朋友都係度拜年，而佢呢個朋友就係係交通津貼熱線度返緊工。<br />\n<br />\n佢由同事口中得知大年初一，部門主管發起賭局，負責做庄，同另外幾個同事係度對賭，對住閉路電視都唔理，大聲講大聲笑，其他員工就各做自己野。平時主管都唔會埋你係度做乜架啦。<br />\n<br />\n聽呢位阿嬸朋友講，條熱線開左個幾月，都基本上冇乜電話要處理，日日同同事都係玩手機過日神，開工玩到收工。<br />\n<br />\n我等佢番去返去問下仲請唔請人先，返荔枝角，雖然要轉車出番九龍，但咁舒服既工去邊度搵呀？"},{"pid":"37b6de787365d9c328a4960bd69212385a9dc0d5","tid":1024843,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T01:20:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好快生果放蛇攪鳩佢"},{"pid":"0d5fdd32f05cad0facc8a876c7f899d940a828c3","tid":1024843,"uid":125073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T01:27:34.000Z","msg":"咩工 想apply too"},{"pid":"5f1e7508a5809e0eb7c678f55ab5ea4cf6ea1a9a","tid":1024843,"uid":55950,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"0d5fdd32f05cad0facc8a876c7f899d940a828c3","tid":1024843,"uid":125073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T01:27:34.000Z","msg":"咩工 想apply too"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T01:31:02.000Z","msg":"只係負責解答交通津貼問題炸！"},{"pid":"d15088e775a81c28671c2c02c415334349d2c10f","tid":1024843,"uid":125073,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5f1e7508a5809e0eb7c678f55ab5ea4cf6ea1a9a","tid":1024843,"uid":55950,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"0d5fdd32f05cad0facc8a876c7f899d940a828c3","tid":1024843,"uid":125073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T01:27:34.000Z","msg":"咩工 想apply too"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T01:31:02.000Z","msg":"只係負責解答交通津貼問題炸！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T